---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Smart AI Hacks">
	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16 px-4">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-white text-center">About <span class="text-primary">Smart AI Hacks</span></h1>
		
		<div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-left space-y-8">
			<p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-center">
				Welcome to Smart AI Hacks, your go-to resource for mastering Artificial Intelligence in your daily life.
			</p>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-300">
					We believe that AI shouldn't be complicated. Our mission is to bridge the gap between complex technology and practical usability. We are dedicated to exploring, testing, and sharing the best tools and strategies to help you work smarter, not harder.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">What We Mean by "Hacks"</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-300">
					At Smart AI Hacks, we use the word "hacks" to describe clever shortcuts, productivity tips, and creative problem-solving techniques. Whether it's a refined prompt for ChatGPT, a workflow automation, or a hidden feature in a new AI tool, our goal is to help you "hack" your productivity curve and achieve more in less time.
				</p>
				<div class="bg-darker p-4 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 rounded-r mt-4">
					<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 m-0">
						<strong>Please note:</strong> We are strictly an educational platform focused on productivity and technology. We do not support or provide information on illegal activities or software cracking.
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">What You Will Find Here</h2>
				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
					<div class="bg-surface p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-800">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary mb-2">Prompt Engineering</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-400">Learn how to talk to AI to get the best results.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-surface p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-800">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary mb-2">Tool Reviews</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-400">Honest insights on the latest AI software and apps.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-surface p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-800">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary mb-2">Productivity Workflows</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-400">Step-by-step guides to integrating AI into your business or studies.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-surface p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-800">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-primary mb-2">Tech News</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-400">Stay updated with the fast-paced world of Artificial Intelligence.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary mb-4">Who We Are</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-300">
					We are a team of tech enthusiasts and AI explorers passionate about the future of work. We test everything we write about to ensure you get accurate and actionable advice.
				</p>
			</section>

			<div class="text-center mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-800">
				<p class="text-lg font-medium text-white">Thank you for visiting, and letâ€™s unlock the potential of AI together!</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
